Titolo: Loop Hero

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Loop Hero is a 2021 endless RPG developed by Russian studio Four Quarters and published by Devolver Digital. The game takes place in a randomly generated world where the player changes the world by placing cards instead of directly controlling a character. The game released for Microsoft Windows, MacOS, and Linux on March 4, 2021. A Nintendo Switch version released on December 9, 2021.